s guidance for 2020 full-year adjusted diluted earnings per share (EPS) to be in a range of $4.30 to $4.38. This range represents a growth rate of 2% to 4% fr" /><link type="image/x-icon" rel="icon" media="" href="//s204.q4cdn.com/505541855/files/favicon.ico" />
